result.execSummary:
The defendant Adam R. Pecha was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Adam R. Pecha is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Adam R. Pecha was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
  • Adam R. Pecha was found guilty of Criminal Damage to Property, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 943.01(1).
